parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger occupancy sensor mat can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the deactivation of the passenger airbag, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag light illuminates
the passenger airbag is forced off
the seat belt light is on
the passenger restraint system malfunction warning appears on the dashboard
the airbag warning indicator illuminates
and the seat belt chime sounds.
